"don’t motivate others to be ethical."

msgctxt "an5.106:3.4"
msgid "attānupekkhī ca hoti, no parānupekkhī;"
msgstr "And they watch themselves, but don’t watch others."

msgctxt "an5.106:3.5"
msgid "ettāvatāpi kho, ānanda, bhikkhu saṃghe viharanto phāsuṃ vihareyyā”ti."
msgstr ""
