#. VAR: āsavānañca → āsavānaṃ (bj, pts1, mr)
msgctxt "an5.106:6.7"
msgid ""
"āsavānañca khayā anāsavaṃ cetovimuttiṃ paññāvimuttiṃ diṭṭheva dhamme sayaṃ "
"abhiññā sacchikatvā upasampajja viharati;"
msgstr ""
"And they realize the undefiled freedom of heart and freedom by wisdom in "
"this very life. And they live having realized it with their own insight due "
"to the ending of defilements."

msgctxt "an5.106:6.8"
msgid "ettāvatāpi kho, ānanda, bhikkhu saṃghe viharanto phāsuṃ vihareyya."
msgstr ""
