#. <a class="sc" id="sc7"></a>
msgctxt "an5.106:7.1"
msgid ""
"Imamhā cāhaṃ, ānanda, phāsuvihārā añño phāsuvihāro uttaritaro vā paṇītataro "
"vā natthīti vadāmī”ti."
msgstr ""
"And I say that there is no better or finer way of living comfortably than "
"this.”"

